 API Server
- Can run as:
  1. Static pod (kubelet reads /etc/kubernetes/manifests/kube-apiserver.yaml)
  2. Systemd process (binary running directly)
  3. Container started outside k8s (systemd or startup scripts)
- Must exist before kubelet can manage pods.
- Control plane components (kube-apiserver, kube-scheduler, kube-controller-manager, etcd) are critical, sometimes outside normal pod control.

